810
00:44:16,175 --> 00:44:17,959
[MUSIC RISES]

811
00:44:18,307 --> 00:44:20,745
[SCREAMS]

812
00:44:20,832 --> 00:44:22,050
Mom!

813
00:44:22,137 --> 00:44:23,312
It's okay.

814
00:44:25,314 --> 00:44:27,577
[HAUNTING MUSIC PLAYING]

815
00:44:27,708 --> 00:44:31,799
[SCREAMING]

816
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:35,237
No! [SCREAMS]

817
00:44:35,324 --> 00:44:37,718
[SCREAMS]
[FIRE SIZZLES]

818
00:44:37,805 --> 00:44:40,373
[PATTY SCREAMS]

819
00:44:40,939 --> 00:44:41,983
