820
00:44:43,506 --> 00:44:45,900
Hey! Come on!
[SCREAMS]

821
00:44:45,987 --> 00:44:47,119
ELLIS: We gotta go!

822
00:44:47,902 --> 00:44:48,947
Go!

823
00:44:51,863 --> 00:44:52,994
DONNA: We have to run.

824
00:44:53,125 --> 00:44:54,604
No matter what happens,

825
00:44:54,692 --> 00:44:55,910
we have to--
TABITHA: Donna!

826
00:44:55,997 --> 00:44:58,130
Donna! Donna, no!
Donna! Donna!

827
00:44:58,521 --> 00:44:59,653
[DONNA GRUNTS]

828
00:45:01,046 --> 00:45:02,264
[CHOKES]

829
00:45:04,136 --> 00:45:06,442
[MUSIC RISES]

830
00:45:06,529 --> 00:45:07,792
[TABITHA GRUNTS]
[GROWLS]

831
00:45:07,879 --> 00:45:09,837
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]
[GASPS]

832
00:45:10,751 --> 00:45:13,493
[BREATHES RAPIDLY]

833
00:45:14,537 --> 00:45:15,713
[THUDS]

834
00:45:17,236 --> 00:45:20,456
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

835
00:45:24,634 --> 00:45:26,636
Donna! Hey, are you okay?

836
00:45:26,724 --> 00:45:28,508
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

837
00:45:28,638 --> 00:45:30,858
[GRUNTS, PANTS]

838
00:45:30,945 --> 00:45:35,384
[PANTING]

839
00:45:35,471 --> 00:45:36,821
