840
00:45:36,908 --> 00:45:38,431
[MUSIC FADES]

841
00:45:38,518 --> 00:45:39,737
I remembered.

842
00:45:40,781 --> 00:45:42,914
I remembered how to hurt them.

843
00:45:43,001 --> 00:45:44,567
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

844
