858
00:47:53,348 --> 00:47:54,393
Fuck.

859
00:47:55,829 --> 00:47:57,875
Boyd. Boyd!

860
00:47:59,920 --> 00:48:00,834
Boyd.

861
00:48:00,965 --> 00:48:02,749
[DRAMATIC MUSICAL STING]
[SCREAMS]

862
00:48:02,836 --> 00:48:04,011
