874
00:48:30,081 --> 00:48:31,996
Okay. Okay.

875
00:48:32,648 --> 00:48:34,824
Okay. All right. Huh?
Hey!

876
00:48:35,347 --> 00:48:37,610
I will drag you out of here
if I fucking have to.

877
00:48:37,697 --> 00:48:39,177
Okay. All right. Okay.

878
00:48:39,264 --> 00:48:41,919
[EERIE MUSIC CONTINUES]

879
00:48:42,267 --> 00:48:44,399
[JADE BREATHES HEAVILY]

880
00:49:00,720 --> 00:49:01,851
