the smart one, were you?

892
00:50:03,652 --> 00:50:05,741
[YELLS]

893
00:50:08,788 --> 00:50:11,008
No! No! No, no, no, no!

894
00:50:11,747 --> 00:50:14,576
[YELLS] No, no!

895
00:50:14,663 --> 00:50:16,274
[GROANS]

896
00:50:16,361 --> 00:50:18,058
Get the fuck off of me!

897
00:50:18,798 --> 00:50:20,321
